name: DUX 1.5
overview: DUX Version 1.5 features new re-balanced gameplay as well as a brand new 16-bit soundtrack created by Andre Naumann and Marco Groß DUX is better than ever! Get yourself back into the high-res bullet-spraying action with insta-respawns. Enjoy a constant 60 fps across 6 stages, consisting of 30+ fully animated CGI enemies and 6 fully animated (and massive) bosses!
